%C A006066 Ed Pegg's web page gives the upper bound for a(6) as 8. But by considering all possible arrangements of 6 lines - the sixth term of A048872 - one can see that 8 is impossible. - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Nov 11 2007
%C A006066 Although they are somewhat similar, this sequence is strictly different from A084935, since A084935(12) = 48 exceeds the upper bound on a(12) from A032765. - _Floor van Lamoen_, Nov 16 2005
%C A006066 The name is sometimes incorrectly entered as "Kodon" triangles.
%C A006066 Named after the Japanese puzzle expert and mathematics teacher Kobon Fujimura (1903-1983). - _Amiram Eldar_, Jun 19 2021
